{"tid":1449911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:20:03.000Z","uid":229453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc87dc5eb531e3737a585e9dce4a83fc9665db73","tid":1449911,"uid":229453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=02781087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=6893e03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=e7edd923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=6893e03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"92ba685d7f89b46fdb91a7dcdf31e0805b1f622e","tid":1449911,"uid":229453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ac25f309222ea8d31127a15cc2d82ac6498e1039","tid":144991